title: Little Diggers Series Kid Safe Poly Garden Shovel
description: Little Diggers are fully functional tools made just for kids. Kids learn by imitation and this kid safe garden shovel is the perfect tool to get them interested in gardening and playing outside. Unlike metal tools, Little Diggers tools are built from a soft, yet durable plastic that is kid safe (non-metal). Little Diggers are offered in bright, vibrant colors that will not rust. Encourage your kids to play outdoors with a Little Diggers garden shovel and other kid safe products by Emsco.
